\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb0\sa240\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Note Groups are special forms of connectors, used for grouping, that may be placed above, below, to the right or left of a group of notes.   Octave groups, hairpins, pedal brackets, voltas, and other brackets of various types fall into this category.\par
